				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Fella's, why go through all the trouble trying to clear Throne Room in Cazic??? I found an easier way to get great items like this! What I did was camp a barbarian named Battledragun. He is a warrior and can be found in many zones, just do a /who! Anyways, after blastin him real good when he limped out of Unrest with a electrocution shock which finished him, I looted this nice item. The unfortunete thing was battledragun had some other nice bronze pieces, and lots of other magical items to choose from. <BR>
Now after killing this dumb npc, you will get /tells from him saying 'YOU PIECE OF S$#%, YOU R GONNA DIE! COME BACK YOU F&amp;%$!&quot;. Of course, always be polite and respond &quot;Pardon me?&quot; or &quot;I'm sorry, I was told you drop a piece of armor I'm looking for, for a wizard quest&quot;. His response may be &quot;U F&amp;%$ING A$&amp;^%%^&amp; (he is very rude this npc) I HAD NO HP LEFT, AND LIKE A &lt;beep&gt;ing &lt;beep&gt;, U BACKSTABBED ME!&quot;. Reply that your not a rogue, and you don't have backstabbing abilities. Well, that's how I got my item. I'm not sure <BR>
if battledragun spawns on your server, but he spawns on Vallon Zek. Also, Feinder (a woodelf druid) drops a nice vest to go along with that cloak....a Lockjaw vest. That npc really gave me some tells, most of it would have to be sensored also. Oh well, that's it! Good Hunting!<BR>
<BR>
